693
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:25,320
I am not allowed to ring the bell either.

694
00:30:26,150 --> 00:30:26,840
What about us?

695
00:30:27,350 --> 00:30:28,230
Both of you have no restrictions.

696
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:29,680
