748
00:32:22,960 --> 00:32:23,920
No, no, no. It's nothing.

749
00:32:24,630 --> 00:32:26,150
What are you waiting for? Continue your training.

750
00:32:28,990 --> 00:32:29,840
To reminder both of you.

